{
  "stem": "3874.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, of course, counsellors would tell us what was happening, anyway.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They-- the organization was, I think, very good in not trying to hide the difficulty from the children.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But primarily, the nucleus was still German and Austrian kids at the time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, because they kept opening more homes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I found out later on they just opened more homes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, where they got the money from, I really don't know at the time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'm still reading about the--about the finances.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I do know that that Baron de Rothschild, for instance, is one of the people who was involved in-- in financing the operations.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Although he had one of the homes, Chateau Legette, he financed all by himself until he left France in 1941-- probably early '41.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And turned those kids over to the OSE, so that those homes no longer existed and it was all part of the OSE.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In a few days-- well, of course, the war continued on, and things didn't get any better obviously-- but, I mean, it was still a reasonably good life.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I remember writing to my parents, asking them for things, like would you please send me a toy, a particular thing which I wanted, or some clothes or something.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And in retrospect, I mean, I-- you know, now that I'm grown, as soon as I became more mature, I realized that that's not the thing to have done, because they were in dire straits themselves.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they, of course, want-- want to do everything for the children.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But they thought possibly I was hurting, I was suffering, whatever it was-- which was really not the case at the time.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
